{
  "stem": "8072.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave us some food over there, some rations, something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly what, but they gave us some food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A soup and a portion of bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the bread was always fresh.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They made us fresh, stale.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You swallowed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You ate it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They would have give you some, you know, small portion.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They gave you to just trying to keep you alive, but not to live.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we wound up in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Also by train.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also by train, you know, because it was quite a distance.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it took another few days to go to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then in Dachau, we-- again, we weren't in the main camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We was in an outskirt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that camp was just being finished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't even finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was like-- [CLEARS THROAT] Basically, what it was, it was-- it was in the woods.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were-- we had to still clear the trees and stumps and everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the way the barracks were was on the ground, like you take, take the ground.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Dig a ditch in the middle, you know, so like, you have-- and the ground was the bed on either side.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was like a triangle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The roof was a triangle with like, wood or-- whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they had a stove right in the middle, just one little stove to keep-- it was supposed to keep you warm.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they had about 50, or 60 people in that-- in these little barracks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think we must have a blanket or something to cover.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But again, it wasn't-- it was already in November.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'44.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was snowing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was freezing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you didn't have any warm clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
